%p.article-content
  = "Dear #{@user.first_name.capitalize.strip},"
%p.article-content
  In an effort to provide the best possible service to our community, we automatically decline any enquiries that are not responded to within 24 hours.
%p.article-content
  We understand that this can be disappointing, and would love to hear your suggestions on how we could improve your experience as a host.
%p.article-content
  Many thanks for your understanding.
%p.article-content The PetHomeStay Team

%h3 Booking Details
%p.article-content
  = "Booking from #{@booking.check_in_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)} #{@booking.check_in_time.strftime("%H:%M")} to #{@booking.check_out_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)} #{@booking.check_out_time.strftime("%H:%M")}"
%p.article-content
  = "Guest Name: #{@guest.first_name.capitalize} #{@guest.last_name.capitalize}"
%p.article-content
  = "Pet Name: #{@guest.pet.name.capitalize}"
%p.article-content
  = "Potential earnings: #{number_to_currency(@booking.subtotal)}"